    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这不是一款普通的种田游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这里，你不是点界面、按按钮去劳动，而是用打字把你的美好生活一点点“写出来”。采集、钓鱼、烹饪美食、经营餐厅、结识伙伴……所有的一切都由打字驱动。在一次次充满节奏的敲击声中，你会不知不觉间进入心流，忘掉时间，感受平静与满足。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335690/extras/294f0f04bc729c6e57caa43d56660b56.poster.avif?t=1770483445\" width=854 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335690/extras/294f0f04bc729c6e57caa43d56660b56.webm?t=1770483445\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335690/extras/294f0f04bc729c6e57caa43d56660b56.mp4?t=1770483445\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>餐厅经营</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将掌管一家温馨的小餐厅。透过采集、耕种、钓鱼等方式获取新鲜食材，为小镇居民烹制佳肴，带给他们幸福时刻。你还可利用木材、矿石不断升级餐厅，丰富经营体验，拓展更多创意菜色。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335690/extras/3e2e62fa2fd9f8ccd3efc428e2a1bbcc.poster.avif?t=1770483445\" width=854 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335690/extras/3e2e62fa2fd9f8ccd3efc428e2a1bbcc.webm?t=1770483445\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335690/extras/3e2e62fa2fd9f8ccd3efc428e2a1bbcc.mp4?t=1770483445\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>小镇伙伴</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这里有许多性格独特的邻居与旅人。你将走进他们的故事，与他们结交、互助，用美食治愈他们，帮助他们打开心扉，实现梦想。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335690/extras/623cc168574bd166f95c9909b5c7929c.poster.avif?t=1770483445\" width=854 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335690/extras/623cc168574bd166f95c9909b5c7929c.webm?t=1770483445\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335690/extras/623cc168574bd166f95c9909b5c7929c.mp4?t=1770483445\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>庄园养成</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >经营菜地与果园，扩建鱼池与畜棚，让庄园一点点长成只属于你的理想田园。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335690/extras/3ec67ff873893d4476ae2ebbc4668376.poster.avif?t=1770483445\" width=854 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335690/extras/3ec67ff873893d4476ae2ebbc4668376.webm?t=1770483445\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335690/extras/3ec67ff873893d4476ae2ebbc4668376.mp4?t=1770483445\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >小镇与周边藏着许多神秘区域，等待你去发现与探访。除了发现奇观、收集道具、改造村庄，你还可以把旅途中遇见的奇妙故事与历史带回博物馆，整理成展品与记录，让更多人认识这片充满温情的土地。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335690/extras/269c6751aead078ea326c554ed6e4009.poster.avif?t=1770483445\" width=854 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335690/extras/269c6751aead078ea326c554ed6e4009.webm?t=1770483445\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335690/extras/269c6751aead078ea326c554ed6e4009.mp4?t=1770483445\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>打字与语言学习</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏内容覆盖从字母、单词到句子、篇章的多种打字与语言练习形式。同时支持多种显示语言与打字语言，并可分别独立切换。你会在轻松游玩的过程中不知不觉提升打字速度与语言能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335690/extras/0408007454cb5cd1a6e9f63e347e665d.poster.avif?t=1770483445\" width=854 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335690/extras/0408007454cb5cd1a6e9f63e347e665d.webm?t=1770483445\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335690/extras/0408007454cb5cd1a6e9f63e347e665d.mp4?t=1770483445\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >其他特性：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >伙伴友好度：与小镇伙伴关系递进，解锁故事、功能。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扩展地图：森林、矿洞、海岛。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >节日活动玩法：钓鱼节、万圣节……</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >……</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎加入我们的社群，一起聊天、一起把游戏打磨得更好。你的反馈对我们非常重要！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在商店页面右侧点击社群链接即可加入。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
